<plot>The identity of Indian families living in the U.S. and the cross cultural differences in evolution. Do Indians, having migrated from their native land, adapt to the difference in culture and are they ready to give up their inherent cultural inhibitions? "Karma, Confessions &amp; Holi" is a film about Indian families, their relationships with fellow Americans, their own internal and inter-personal conflicts.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?287264</url></doc>
